WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.140
What did the Lord show me last night concerning Donald Trump?

00:00:02.140 --> 00:00:04.148
I saw him at a ballroom party.

00:00:04.148 --> 00:00:06.210
I saw him; he was celebrating.

00:00:06.210 --> 00:00:07.950
He had a tuxedo on.

00:00:09.400 --> 00:00:13.564
They were all dressed up, but he had a goblet, a glass in his hand.

00:00:14.247 --> 00:00:19.741
I did not see anybody putting anything in his glass.

00:00:20.203 --> 00:00:26.588
I don't add to or take away from anything in a vision.

00:00:26.588 --> 00:00:32.590
I saw a glass in his hand and it was focused on this glass.

00:00:33.688 --> 00:00:37.020
I don't want to add; like I said, you add to it and you get flaky.

00:00:37.020 --> 00:00:37.280
Don't.

00:00:37.280 --> 00:00:38.124
This is what I saw.

00:00:38.124 --> 00:00:42.160
I saw him holding the glass and then I saw him having a massive heart attack.

00:00:42.160 --> 00:00:46.217
I saw something wrong in his heart.

00:00:46.971 --> 00:00:59.137
I saw the waitstaff and I don't know what happened between the glass and the goblet and him, why he would do this, but he was holding it.

00:00:59.137 --> 00:01:07.973
Now, all the doctors say he's okay, but he was holding a drink and I saw the drink and the vision was focused on that cup.

00:01:08.320 --> 00:01:10.880
The Lord said, 'Pray over his food.

00:01:10.880 --> 00:01:12.800
Pray over his drink.

00:01:12.800 --> 00:01:16.880
Pray over the parties.

00:01:16.880 --> 00:01:20.640
Pray over him as he has these get-togethers.

00:01:20.640 --> 00:01:26.360
' So, instantaneously, you can add to it and say, 'Well, that's probably they're going to try to poison him.

00:01:26.360 --> 00:01:26.890
' I don't know.

00:01:27.640 --> 00:01:29.424
That's not what the Lord said.

00:01:29.424 --> 00:01:43.280
All I saw was a cup with gold and I saw the drink and I saw the food and I saw the party and I saw everybody dressed up and then I saw him taking it to his lips.

00:01:43.280 --> 00:01:46.053
And then he went down.

00:01:46.053 --> 00:01:49.672
So, does that mean the poison is in his glass?

00:01:49.672 --> 00:01:50.420
I don't know.

00:01:50.420 --> 00:01:51.920
I can't answer that.

00:01:51.920 --> 00:01:53.800
But the Lord said, 'Pray over his drink.

00:01:53.800 --> 00:01:56.800
' Then I saw Don Jr.

00:01:56.800 --> 00:02:02.030
again with the white outfit on with flashes and him being shot in the chest.

00:02:02.030 --> 00:02:04.960
I saw praying over his son.

00:02:04.960 --> 00:02:07.378
He was at a party and event again.

00:02:07.378 --> 00:02:13.920
And then I saw the Secret Service; he said pray for their attentiveness even at a party.

00:02:13.920 --> 00:02:17.040
Pray for their attentiveness.

00:02:17.040 --> 00:02:24.000
Watching the crowd, watching his surroundings, praying for protection over him and his family.

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:27.040
So that's what we do.

00:02:27.040 --> 00:02:41.679
Interceding for Donald Trump, for him to live long and finish strong and finish what God has called him to do, that no weapon formed against him will prosper, or his children, because it would cause great grief and he would not...

00:02:41.679 --> 00:02:55.509
I'm telling you I've seen the outcome of what happens whenever his son was fatally wounded and the Lord said to me, 'You must pray for his children's safety.

00:02:55.509 --> 00:03:09.911
' He was so grieving, grief-stricken, he could not function the rest of the term because he was grieving so much for the loss of his son.

00:03:09.911 --> 00:03:14.107
He was not able to even hardly walk and I saw Melania.

00:03:14.107 --> 00:03:26.940
I remember I told you all I saw his daughter dressed up in solid black and they were going to the funeral service where the inauguration was there by the White House, that church, it was like a big church service like that.

00:03:30.299 --> 00:03:34.330
And they were going to this service and there were people from everywhere.

00:03:34.330 --> 00:03:47.280
And I saw him walking down and he got out of the Beast and he was walking down and I remember him walking to the funeral reception, the service, and he was weeping.

00:03:47.280 --> 00:03:48.026
He was weeping.

00:03:49.519 --> 00:03:52.040
He could not keep himself held up.

00:03:52.040 --> 00:03:54.548
They were helping him walk.

00:03:54.548 --> 00:03:56.159
It was awful.

00:03:56.159 --> 00:04:02.560
So when I have that stern of a vision, if I see something that clear, I've not stopped praying since.

00:04:02.560 --> 00:04:05.542
Interceding for the protection of Don Jr.

00:04:05.542 --> 00:04:19.240
, over Kai, over Eric, over Barron, over all of them, Tiffany, over Ivanka, that God's hand would be on their family and on his marriage.

00:04:19.240 --> 00:04:20.695
So that's what we do.

00:04:20.695 --> 00:04:21.775
We continue to do this.

00:04:21.775 --> 00:04:26.630
And I saw an attack against his buildings more than once now.

00:04:28.764 --> 00:04:42.820
I keep seeing them trying to attack his main attractions, you know, his Trump towers and hotels and golf courses and just interceding because of the plans to try to rob him financially.

00:04:42.820 --> 00:05:01.851
But not only that, that caused a distraction to this nation by hurting his assets.

00:05:12.400 --> 00:05:17.576
Where is this place?

00:05:18.880 --> 00:05:25.670
I see white drapes.

00:05:25.680 --> 00:05:27.188
I see chandeliers.

00:05:28.696 --> 00:05:30.525
He's wearing a black tie.

00:05:30.525 --> 00:05:34.400
He's wearing a black tuxedo again.

00:05:34.400 --> 00:05:35.840
I see the tuxedo.

00:05:35.840 --> 00:05:38.743
He has something in his hand.

00:05:38.743 --> 00:05:40.533
Looks like a drink.

00:05:40.533 --> 00:05:45.943
We know Trump doesn't drink alcohol.

00:05:45.943 --> 00:05:51.173
I see this glass that has gold at the top.

00:05:51.173 --> 00:05:54.240
There's gold at the top of this glass.

00:05:54.240 --> 00:05:56.000
That's actual real gold.

00:05:56.000 --> 00:06:00.064
It's like a golden glass, a goblet like fine crystal.

00:06:01.248 --> 00:06:03.248
There's white tablecloths.

00:06:03.248 --> 00:06:09.919
There's white tables with beautiful centerpiece arrangements.

00:06:12.672 --> 00:06:15.770
These women are dressed up in ball gowns.

00:06:15.770 --> 00:06:17.466
Men are in black tuxedos.

00:06:17.466 --> 00:06:19.325
They're all dressed up very nice.

00:06:19.325 --> 00:06:21.908
We pray a protection over President Trump.

00:06:21.908 --> 00:06:23.646
We pray over him.

00:06:23.646 --> 00:06:25.520
We pray over his sons.

00:06:25.520 --> 00:06:27.291
We pray over his daughters.

00:06:27.291 --> 00:06:28.949
We pray over his family.

00:06:30.270 --> 00:06:39.880
We pray a hedge of protection around and about them, over every party, over every get-together, any kind of celebration.

00:06:39.880 --> 00:06:50.400
We pray a hedge of protection that his Secret Service is more attentive even to the ones that are in the room.

00:06:50.400 --> 00:06:57.270
Just because they pass security, the ones in the room...

00:06:57.280 --> 00:07:01.820
I don't understand it in the natural.

00:07:01.820 --> 00:07:05.067
We thank you Lord that President Trump is protected.

00:07:12.240 --> 00:07:15.680
No weapon formed against him would prosper.

00:07:18.880 --> 00:07:30.780
Every plot, every plan will be uncovered in the name of Jesus, at black-tie events.

00:07:34.160 --> 00:07:36.320
We pray over Don Jr.

00:07:39.467 --> 00:07:40.213
The blood of Jesus surround him in Jesus' name.

00:07:51.439 --> 00:07:53.268
He will finish his course.

00:07:53.268 --> 00:07:58.150
He will live long and finish strong.

00:07:59.560 --> 00:08:06.080
We pray over his heart, over every artery, over the valves of the heart.

00:08:10.100 --> 00:08:17.440
We call protection in the name of Jesus over drinks.

00:08:19.680 --> 00:08:21.724
We pray over the food.

00:08:21.724 --> 00:08:23.733
We bless his food.

00:08:23.733 --> 00:08:25.519
I believe we can pray over his food.

00:08:25.759 --> 00:08:28.520
I pray over his drink and the goblet.

00:08:28.850 --> 00:08:35.627
We pray over his drinks, over everything that is ever handed to him.

00:08:54.380 --> 00:09:02.070
You said we could eat or drink any deadly thing and it would not harm us.

00:09:02.080 --> 00:09:08.080
Everything we drink, everything we eat, we thank you Lord.

00:09:08.080 --> 00:09:11.859
You see that it affects the heart.

00:09:11.859 --> 00:09:20.880
Like everything we drink, everything he eats, he's protected.

00:09:34.800 --> 00:09:38.959
I pray over him as he drinks these things.

00:09:38.959 --> 00:09:56.480
That Father, any kind of poison, any kind of thing, nothing comes nigh, even to make it look like an accident, like it's just natural.

00:10:07.839 --> 00:10:10.583
Every plot, every plan, every pursuit.

00:10:10.583 --> 00:10:15.600
I thank you, Lord, that you protect President Trump.

00:10:15.600 --> 00:10:18.826
That you raise up a hedge around and about him.

00:10:18.826 --> 00:10:27.417
Father, I thank you that his Secret Service are so heightened and alert, they never let their guard down.

00:10:27.417 --> 00:10:34.274
They are like a bulldog the whole time.

00:10:34.274 --> 00:10:41.119
Always watching everybody's hands, always watching the people who are bringing refreshments.

00:10:43.200 --> 00:10:51.519
Whoever is over that, I thank you Lord that they're smart, they're watching over what he eats and what he drinks.

00:10:58.559 --> 00:11:05.360
They must not become lax; they must protect our President.

00:11:06.617 --> 00:11:09.131
I pray over Mar-a-Lago.

00:11:09.760 --> 00:11:18.304
I pray over any events, over his family, over Don Jr.

00:11:19.216 --> 00:11:24.764
, over Kai, even over Barron, even over this boy.

00:11:24.764 --> 00:11:35.519
We pray a hedge around and about his son that the Kennedy curse would be broken.
